data.description: This home offers everything you could ever want. We are pleased to welcome you home. When you arrive, you will be greeted with a beautifully landscaped yard and a private backyard oasis. It has an impressive curb appeal that will greet you at first glance. In the grand two-story foyer adjacent to the dining room with coffered ceilings, you can create unforgettable memories with your loved ones. With granite countertops and ample cabinetry, the eat-in kitchen will surely be the heart of your home. It's open to the family room with a fireplace. On the main level, this home features a flexible-use room and full bathroom, perfect for guests or multi-generational families. A large loft upstairs can be used as a playroom, home office, or additional living area. The primary bedroom will feel like a retreat every day. The oversized layout provides plenty of space for relaxation, while the en-suite bathroom is a peaceful oasis. Two additional spacious bedrooms on the upper level ensure that everyone in the household has their retreat. There is a deck overlooking the expansive backyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining, relaxing, or simply enjoying the beautiful surroundings. Perfectly situated just minutes from the interstate and Hartsfield airport, this home offers unmatched convenience for commuters and frequent travelers. Take advantage of the opportunity to make this exquisite home your own. Beyond the walls of this exquisite home, a world of amenities awaits you. Take advantage of the convenience of a clubhouse, ideal for entertaining or socializing with neighbors. In summer, you can take a refreshing dip in the pool, play some tennis, or wander leisurely along the sidewalks. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and discover this home's luxury and charm. Preferred Closing Attorney The Hawes Law Firm
